Privacy Policy for OffGrid Survival
Effective Date: 09/04/25

OffGrid Survival does not collect any personal or personally identifiable information. Our app exclusively relies on the built-in encryption and data protection mechanisms provided by Apple's iOS frameworks (for example, MCSession with encryptionPreference set to .required). We do not use any third-party tracking, analytics, or advertising services.

Data Collection
Personal Data:
We do not collect any personal data or personally identifiable information.

Crash Data:
In the event of a crash, minimal crash data may be automatically collected by Appleâ€™s systems to improve overall app stability. This data is managed entirely by Apple and is not accessible to us.

Analytics and Tracking:
We do not employ any additional analytics or tracking services that collect data about your usage of the app.

Data Usage
All data collected (if any) is used solely for the purpose of enhancing the functionality, performance, and stability of the app.

No user data is shared with any third parties.

Data Security
OffGrid Survival uses the standard security and encryption protocols available in iOS. Our app does not implement any custom or additional encryption algorithms.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.

Contact
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us via the App Store support channel.
